title: Minutemen Discography
description:
The Minutemen are an 80s punk band which, quite simply, own. Got a few of these albums from someone else, so credit given where credit is needed.

1980 - Paranoid Time - 320kbps
1981 - Joy - 320kbps
1981 - The Punch Line - 192kbps
1982 - Bean-Spill - 320kbps
1983 - What Makes A Man Start Fires? - 192kbps
1983 - Buzz or Howl Under The Influence of Heat - 224kbps
1984 - The Politics of Time - 320kbps
1984 - Double Nickels on the Dime - ~320kbps VBR
1985 - Project: Mersh - 224kbps
1985 - 3-Way Tie (For Last) - 192kbps
